```&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;</description></item><item><title>hugo博客添加数据统计页面</title><link>https://geekswg.js.cool/posts/2026/blog-stats/</link><pubDate>Sat, 24 Jan 2026 15:22:51 +0800</pubDate><author>geekswg@qq.com (geekswg)</author><guid>https://geekswg.js.cool/posts/2026/blog-stats/</guid><category domain="https://geekswg.js.cool/categories/theme/">theme</category><description>&lt;p&gt;给你的博客添加统计页面，展示你的博客数据统计信息。&lt;a href="https://geekswg.js.cool/stats/" target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer"&gt;点击这里&lt;i class="fa-solid fa-external-link-alt fa-fw fa-xs ms-1 text-secondary" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;预览效果。&lt;/p&gt;
